caption.paragraph:
On following pages: 90. Unicolored Tree-rat (
Phyllomys
unicolon; 91. Patton's Atlantic Tree-rat (
Phyllomys
patton); 92. Serra da Mantiqueira Atlantic Tree-rat (
Phyllomys mantiqueirensis
); 93. Lund’s Atlantic Tree-rat (
Phyllomys lundi
): 94. Kerr's Atlantic Tree-rat (
Phyllomys kerri
); 95. Long-furred Atlantic Tree-rat (
Phyllomys medius
); 96. Giant Atlantic Tree-rat (
Phyllomys thomasi
); 97. Drab Atlantic Tree-rat (
Phyllomys dasythrix
); 98. Southern Atlantic Treerat (
Phyllomys
sulinus); 99. Black-spined Atlantic Tree-rat (
Phyllomys nigrispinus
).
